column5:
RT @MsPackyetti: “What does Brett Kavanaugh have to hide? What does the White House have to hide? 

Why don’t they want the facts?” 
@SenGi…

Nearly 3,000 American lives were lost because of the administration's incompetent response to Hurricane Maria.

@realDonaldTrump wanted the trappings of the presidency without the responsibility.

We need a 9/11-style independent commission to investigate the failed response.
